80	
81	/**
82	 * parseVerdict(raw, evidence) -> { state, verdict, reason, disproof }
83	 *   state    the closed three-state: 'violation' | 'needs_review' | 'pass'.
84	 *   verdict  the normalised model verdict ('breach'|'no_breach'|'insufficient') or null if unparseable.
85	 *   reason   a short human-readable cause (the model's own reason when present, else a fixed default).
86	 *   disproof the verbatim disproof span (only on a `pass`; null otherwise).
